data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bed, 2 and a half bath home situated on a large corner lot, tucked away in the quiet subdivision of Sunset Oaks Addition.  Enjoy the security and privacy of a gated community, located close to 820 for convenient access, minutes from downtown Fort Worth. As you step inside the foyer, you're greeted with an open primary dining and additional seating area in the front, sectioned off from the open main living room and kitchen. The modern and inviting kitchen has been recently upgraded and offers 42 inch shaker cabinets, with a huge island and walk-in pantry. The large oversized bedrooms are upstairs with master and ensuite. Leading to the back yard is a fully enclosed sunroom, surrounded with natural light from the expansive windows. The sunroom addition is fully finished with AC and provides the perfect space for peaceful relaxation. The home offers a separate utility, with garage access. New AC unit, New water heater, and newly installed gutters!
